{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"在布达佩斯的广场上","authors":["马其"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":8,"day":31}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在布达佩斯的广场上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候，爱好和平民主的人民把他们的目光凝聚在东欧布达佩斯的广场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布达佩斯的市民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥塞在大街上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿着漂亮的新装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要看看来自异国的年青人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看他们怎么欢渡佳节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要准备献给他们鲜花和吻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在布达佩斯的广场上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十多国的青年代表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不同的肤色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不同的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉着手，并着肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱着，亲吻着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在布达佩斯的广场上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱好和平民主的年青一代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摆出了他们的阵营"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"检阅他们自己的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在空中飞扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在红旗下面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有千千万万的青年人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他们高举着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民领袖们的巨像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷动的掌声起来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个苏联少年出现在播音机前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召世界青年反对战争贩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个中国的年青人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在台上宣布了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝在中国的破产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个自由希腊的青年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希腊人民不屈服的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联青年们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用集体大合唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱出了社会主义的幸福歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国青年用朴素的舞蹈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显示出新中国工人的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的黑人少年唱一首歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们听见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑人被压迫的悲惨境遇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲演，歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞蹈，艺术竞赛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运动会，游行示威"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们在欢乐里渡佳节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们在佳节里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习，交换革命经验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几万人齐声合唱国际歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“起来饥寒交迫的奴隶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来全世界的罪人！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几万人齐声呼喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“斯大林，毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉科西，乌拉！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一支保卫和平的铁军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支队伍代表着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春，代表着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类伟大的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"联系他们在一起的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个共同的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为了全人类真正的解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十四日于平"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}